### Welcome to my website!
Meet me! This website just shows you a few things you can learn about me!

### Background
My name is Alexis Pine, currently I am a sophomore attending the University of Maine with a major in Business Management. I am from a small town on the midcoast of Maine in Owls Head. This website shows and shares just a little bit about me!
